<description><![CDATA[Art Sexy Lightbox: this plugin shows photos, photo groups, external pages, Flickr photos, inline content in pretty highly customizable popup window. Please enable plugin in order to use it. <br /><br />Plugin code example:<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;{artsexylightbox path="folder_path"/} - this will read all images from specified folder and display as gallery<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;{artsexylightbox flickr="flickr_user_id"/} - this will read flickr images from specified user and display them as gallery.<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;{artsexylightbox /} - this will add lightbox effect to any link on the page that has rel="sexylightbox" attribute.<br /><br />&copy;&nbsp;<a href="http://www.artetics.com">Artetics.com</a> - Start Point For Your Website.]]></description>
